#             Discord  →  NOTIFY_WEBHOOK=https://discord.com/api/webhooks/...
#             Slack    →  NOTIFY_WEBHOOK=https://hooks.slack.com/services/...
#NOTIFY_WEBHOOK=https://ntfy.sh/averys-op-list
